\frametitle{Polarization \& Closure-Freedom}

How to compile this?
\vspace{1em}
\begin{verbatim}
                   f : Bool → Int → Int
                   f b = case b of True  → λ x. x + 10
                                   False → λ x. x * 10
\end{verbatim}
And this?
\begin{verbatim}
                   f : Int → Int
                   f x :=
                     let g y := x + y;
                     g x + 10
\end{verbatim}
